<h1 id="c:categories" class="tex-chapter"><span data-tag="0000">1</span> Algebraic prerequisites: monoidal categories</h1>

<p>
In this chapter we introduce some of the algebraic language necessary for describing TQFTs, most importantly the notion of a monoidal category. We only give a very brief introduction, referring the reader to books [mac-lane], [etingof-fusion] for details. 
</p>
